originalText.text: Everything was perfect. originalText.text: It was an amazing experience! Vlad was so informative and helped me plan the perfect environment to surprise my girlfriend with a proposal.  When inclement weather threatened to spoil the day he even rescheduled the date and time a few days before to make it all as perfect as it could be.  We got incredibly clear photos over the course of an hour and a video of the actual moment.  Totally worth it and Vlad couldn’t have been more professional or courteous!  Thanks Vlad!

originalText.text: Tatiana and Vlad are great professionals. They had awesome communication, fantastic planning,  prompt execution, to mention but a few of their professional qualities. Vlad captured our most exciting moment and did it stealthily according to plan. I loved that he accommodated me during a challenge as I had missed an exit on my way to Manhattan, New York, which led to a few minutes delay in my proposal. My girlfriend (now fiancée) loved every bit of the plan execution and most of all, she said “Yes!” on Valentine’s Day of 2023.

originalText.text:
Amazing service and amazing delivery!!! I requested their night package at Central Park less than 5 days before the proposal and I was stunned at the delivery and execution. For context I do not live in the US but I found Proposal 007 online through a google search. It took a lot of trust as I had never worked with them before neither do I know personally anyone who had worked with them before. I reached out to Tatiana who was very patient and professional and, without ever meeting the team physically but only talking to Tatiana on the phone and through WhatsApp messages, I booked the Central Park evening package and I was not disappointed! It was such a beautiful moment to mark my fiancé and I’s trip to USA.

They are a real service and they deliver really excellent packages! You don’t have to worry about anything, all you have to do is show up!

Even the pictures they take of the event are so beautiful! Shout out to Vlad the photographer who takes absolutely stunning photos!!

I have rated them 5 stars only because there are no higher ratings to give!!
